name: CP03
description:
Introducing the Lads of Fortune black on black LOF cap. This baseball snapback cap uses the classic idea of designing with black on black. The Lof is a 3d embroidered abbreviation of our name Lads of Fortune. This strong, bold cap will work with all wardrobes. 

The Cap has 3 embroideries:
 
* Front Logo. 
* LHS has our black LOF. 
* Back reads Lads of Fortune. 

Made from 100% cotton drill. Sizes: one size fits all.

name: CP01
description:
Introducing the Lads of Fortune LOF Red Yellow and Blue 3d embroidered snap back baseball cap. Like all our caps at Lads of Fortune we have created simple yet bold designs- using strong graphics, interesting colours and have worked hard to get a quality fit. Cap has 3 embroideries: Front LOF, LHS it has our white LOF Logo found on the front page of our website- on the back Lads of Fortune. 
Made from 100% cotton drill
sizes: one size fits all

name: CP05
description:
Introducing Lads of Fortune anchor logo cap. 

This baseball snapback cap is bright blue and uses a strong contrasting lime and white embroidery. The combination of pop colours and simple emblematic design references graphics of the 50's advertising world when American signage was at its best. 

Cap has 3 embroideries: 
* Front Logo 
* LHS it has our lime Lads of Fortune Logo 
* Back reads Lads of Fortune

Made from 100% cotton drill. Sizes: one size fits all.

name: CP17
description:
Introducing Lads of Fortune black and white wing 12 oz 100% Trucker cap. 

The cap features a white embroidery on black cotton with a flat peak and black mesh at the back. The back is snapback design. Made from 60% cotton 40% nylon. Sizes: one size fits all.

name: CP08
description:
Introducing the Lads of Fortune switch blade baseball snapback. 
Large script logo with blade intersects the A. 
Cap has 3 embroideries: 
* Front Logo with blade 
* LHS it has our white LOF Logo
* Back has two intersecting crossed blades with central diamond  
Cap is Navy Blue with Light grey Embroideries are 3d white red and navy. Made from 100% cotton drill. Sizes: one size fits all

name: KT01

name: JK04
description:
LIMITED EDITION Introducing the Bronze Bomber. 
Come out super styling with this unique bomber styled jacket keeping you warm with the padded lining. The outer shell is 100% nylon with 100% nylon lining and 100% polyester fill. The jacket has some great features that are all unique to Lads of Fortune. Jacquard black ribbed  hem and cuffs.

name: JK03
description:
RUNWAY JACKET
Quality is the focus of this understatedly cool varsity jacket. The colours feature a unique green, with red blue and white highlights to complete the pallete.  Melton body with a nice brushed furry feel- fully lined with a chombre detail on the inside. Keeping with affordability we opted for the arms to be a well-treated super comfy faux leather sleeve- not too heavy so it can work across most seasons. 

The badge motifs are a key feature of this garment; super sized and prominent to reflect the true varsity style- American influenced and classic fit. This piece is a unique one- for the fashion forward not afraid of trying different colours. The fit is pure comfort and the detailing on the front is impressive with Lads of Fortune chain circular embroiderys. 

NOTE WE HAVE ONE LEFT- THERE IS A SMALL BLUE MARK ON SLEEVE ITS AVAILABLE IN A MEDIUM- NO REFUNDS FOR THE MARK AS EXPLAINED HERE

name: JK02
description:
Introducing the black and gold classic Bomber. 

Come out super styling with this unique bomber styled jacket keeping you warm with the padded lining. The outer shell is 100% nylon with 100% nylon lining and 100% polyester fill. The jacket has some great features that are all unique to Lads of Fortune. The front Lads of Fortune LOF in black raised terry-toweling detail and gold satin stitch detail.  

Black and gold embroidered daggers and diamonds badge on one arm. Lads of Fortune embroidered badge on other arm. Jacquard black and gold ribbed stripes on neck hem and cuffs. 

This item is on special order only.  You will be one of only a few lucky people to own this original limited edition jacket. 


To register for one email: ladsoffortune@hotmail.com
Will only Produce 50 so once I hit that mark I order it I will give updates along the way
